u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-R-GREED-CREED-REVIEW-     03-01 0516
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-GREED-CREED-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) 
 UNDATED: only cheaper. 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Dave Ramsey, who has a syndicated financial-counseling show on
44 radio stations, mostly in small and medium-sized markets outside
