   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   PROFILE-BHUTTO (Karachi) _ Eleven years after being swept to
power on the hopes of millions, she spends more time these days in
courtrooms fighting corruption charges than in parliament battling
for her people. By Indira A.R. Lakshmana. (2 takes)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
