<HEADER>
A3333 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-SMOKING-CESSATION     03-01 0850
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SCI-SMOKING-CESSATION-ART-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
NEW THERAPY HELPING SMOKERS QUIT 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Attn: Calif., Minn., Wis., Ky., N.J., N.Y.)   (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.)  
 (af)  
 By HOLCOMB B. NOBLE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
