<SLUG> BC-OLY-IOC-EXPULSIONS-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Additional members examined as IOC grapples with inaccuracies
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving in (a) General News and (s) Sports categories.)
 &HT;    By Melissa Turner
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ At least half a dozen more International Olympic
Committee members are under suspicion for improprities in the Salt
Lake City bribery scandal, the head of an IOC inquiry panel said
Monday.
</P>
<P>
   After a weekend meeting at IOC headquarters in Lausanne,
Switzerland, the head of the six-member commission said they were
