<DOCNO> NYT19990301.0392 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-01 20:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3717 &Cx1f; taf-z
