<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-01 23:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3994 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-NETS-CELTICS-490&AMP;     03-01 0931
